# Worker prompt pack format (LOCKED v1.1)

**trace_tag:** `AUTO-TRACE-RULE-WORKER-PACK-FORMAT-v1.1`  
**agent:** `Auto`  
**Canonical:** `brain-os/contract/WORKER_PROMPT_PACK_FORMAT_LOCKED_v1.md`  
**Tag law:** `brain-os/contract/DOC_TRACE_TAG_FORMAT_LOCKED_v1.md`

## Never

- CHECK / ACT / VERIFY as **separate founder pastes** per sa
- Ceremony micro-queues or STOP-wait between pack lines
- E2E-3 or DEBUG-5 as **standalone extra pastes** (must be inside prompt #3, #5, #6, …)

## Always

- **One prompt = one full turn** (read + implement + verify + closeout in same paste)
- **Every 3rd prompt:** E2E-3 gate inside that paste — full E2E, implement, verify PASS, fix, search missing (last 3 turns)
- **Every 5th prompt:** DEBUG-5 gate inside that paste — full debug, all validators E2E, hub refresh/sync, inbox/queue drift, runtime hygiene
- Default **10 per worker lane**; regenerators must enforce gates

Reject any pack that fails both line tests in the LOCKED doc.
